<span id="freeTextContainer15697228784541321057">This book was a little too long, a bit slow in spots, occasionally repetitive, and there were even a couple of typos -- and I&apos;m <i>still</i> giving it five stars. It was that amazing.</span>
  <span id="freeText15697228784541321057" style="display:none">This book was a little too long, a bit slow in spots, occasionally repetitive, and there were even a couple of typos -- and I'm <i>still</i> giving it five stars. It was that amazing.</span>
