<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7093931-the-condemnation-of-blackness"><img alt="The Condemnation of Blackness: Race, Crime, and the Making of Modern Urban America" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348433553l/7093931._SX98_.jpg" />
