<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/97610.Worse_Than_Slavery"><img alt="Worse Than Slavery: Parchman Farm and the Ordeal of Jim Crow Justice" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1347449924l/97610._SX98_.jpg" />
